quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,5,"Ma lahum bihi min AAilmin walali-aba-ihim kaburat kalimatan takhruju min afwahihimin yaqooloona illa kathiba"
  18,6,"FalaAAallaka bakhiAAun nafsaka AAalaatharihim in lam yu/minoo bihatha alhadeethiasafa"
  18,7,"Inna jaAAalna ma AAalaal-ardi zeenatan laha linabluwahum ayyuhum ahsanuAAamala"
  18,8,"Wa-inna lajaAAiloona maAAalayha saAAeedan juruza"
  18,9,"Am hasibta anna as-habaalkahfi warraqeemi kanoo min ayatinaAAajaba"
  18,10,"Ith awa alfityatu ilaalkahfi faqaloo rabbana atina minladunka rahmatan wahayyi/ lana min amrinarashada"
  18,11,"Fadarabna AAala athanihimfee alkahfi sineena AAadada"
  18,12,"Thumma baAAathnahum linaAAlama ayyualhizbayni ahsa lima labithoo amada"
  18,13,"Nahnu naqussu AAalaykanabaahum bilhaqqi innahum fityatun amanoobirabbihim wazidnahum huda"
  18,14,"Warabatna AAalaquloobihim ith qamoo faqaloo rabbunarabbu assamawati wal-ardilan nadAAuwa min doonihi ilahan laqad qulna ithanshatata"
  18,15,"Haola-i qawmuna ittakhathoomin doonihi alihatan lawla ya/toona AAalayhim bisultaninbayyinin faman athlamu mimmani iftara AAalaAllahi kathiba"
